summary: Sam Darnold, the quarterback for the Minnesota Vikings, has played well recently, leading to speculation about his future and contract negotiations. NFL experts believe Darnold will be highly sought after when he becomes a free agent and predict he could earn a contract worth over $40 million. While the Vikings acknowledge Darnold's value, he has stated that he is not currently focused on negotiating an extension. A recent mic'd-up video highlights Darnold's positive attitude and support for Vikings starting quarterback Kirk Cousins. Despite his impressive play, Darnold has expressed a desire to continue improving and prove he can be a long-term NFL starter.

summary: The Atlanta Falcons and Las Vegas Raiders are set to face off on Monday Night Football, with significant news breaking regarding the starting quarterbacks. The Raiders' decision to start Ridder against his former team has been dubbed "Ridder's Revenge" by Sports Illustrated.
